snippet.title: Undertale Wildfire - Combat Demo Release Date Reveal
snippet.description:
Undertale Wildfire is a fangame following Riley, the human SOUL of Bravery. Get ready to experience a small vertical slice of Wildfire's revamped combat system this August 2024, with PLAYs and Trinkets and more!

Follow Undertale Wildfire on:
- Twitter: https://x.com/UndertaleWldfre
- Gamejolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/undertalewildfire/868658
- Discord: https://discord.gg/nAsmtPZ3w2

Art for teaser by Frigadae, logo animation by evanjamesTM
